  *)
    cat >&2 <<USAGE
usage: bash tool/_n6_lib <sub>
  sub ∈ blockers | roi | arithmetic | derivation | atlas | domains | papers
      | monte_carlo | causal | citations | nexus_dep | loop_rules
      | experiments | falsification | gap | propose | promote | invariants
      | idempotence | manifest | schemas | integrity | engine-hash | emitter-registry
      | audit | audit-summary | audit-retention | claim-effectiveness
